<html lang='en'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <title>Power of Attorney</title>
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <style>
      body {
        background-color: #f0f0f0;
        color: #000;
        font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        -webkit-user-select: none;
        -moz-user-select: none;
        -ms-user-select: none;
        user-select: none;
      }

      .page {
        background: white;
        width: 21cm;
        min-height: 29.7cm;
        padding: 2cm;
        margin: 1cm auto;
        border: 1px solid #d3d3d3;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      h1 {
        text-align: center;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        font-weight: bold;
      }

      .section {
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        text-align: justify;
      }

      .signature-section {
        margin-top: 40px;
      }

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        body {
          background-color: white;
        }
        .page {
          width: 100%;
          min-height: auto;
          margin: 0;
          padding: 20px;
          border: none;
          box-shadow: none;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='page'>
      <h1>Power of Attorney</h1>

      <div class='section' style='text-align: left;'>
        City of
        {{city}},
        {{date}}.
      </div>

      <div class='section'>
        I, a citizen of Ukraine,
        <strong>{{fullName}}</strong>, born on
        {{birthDate}}, taxpayer registration card number
        {{taxId}}, place of residence registered at:
        {{address}}, passport No.
        {{passportNumber}}, issued by
        {{passportIssueAuthority}}
        on
        {{passportIssueDate}}, being fully aware of the meaning of my actions and in accordance with my free will, which
        fully corresponds to my inner intentions, do hereby authorize
        <strong>{{representativeName}}</strong>, born on
        {{representativeBirthDate}}, place of residence registered at:
        {{representativeAddress}},
      </div>

      <div class='section'>
        TO REPRESENT MY INTERESTS in any enterprises, institutions, and organizations, regardless of their
        subordination, form of ownership, and industry affiliation, in bodies of executive power and local
        self-government, in bodies of the state executive service, ministries, agencies, their structural subdivisions,
        state committees, and their subordinate bodies; in embassies and consulates of foreign states in Ukraine; in
        notary offices (private or state), in bodies of justice, including - in justice departments of any level, state
        registration bodies for real property rights, before state registrars of the departments of state registration
        of legal entities, individual entrepreneurs, and public associations, the Department for the Provision of
        Administrative Services, in civil status registration bodies, etc.; in any banking institutions of Ukraine; in
        customs authorities, in any bodies of the migration service, in the bodies of the passport and visa service of
        Ukraine; in prosecution bodies, in internal affairs bodies, the National Police of Ukraine, the Main and
        territorial departments of the National Police of Ukraine and its separate subdivisions, patrol police bodies,
        Territorial Recruitment and Social Support Centers, in other law enforcement agencies of Ukraine; in all
        departments and directorates of the State Agency of Land Resources of Ukraine, branches of the Center of the
        State Land Cadastre of Ukraine, the State Cadastral Registrar of the relevant territorial subdivision of the
        State Geocadastre; in appraisal, expert organizations, address bureaus, in BTI bodies (Bureau of Technical
        Inventory), in urban planning and architecture bodies; in the State Tax authorities, in territorial and
        structural subdivisions of the State Fiscal Service of Ukraine, institutions of the Pension Fund of Ukraine, the
        State Service of Ukraine for Personal Data Protection, statistics bodies, the employment fund, the social
        insurance fund; in all judicial institutions of any level, including appellate, cassation courts, etc.; in
        medical institutions; in housing and communal bodies, services: gas, electricity, water supply, heating, etc.;
        in communication bodies (post offices, telephone companies, etc.) and their branches, before any individuals
        and/or legal entities on matters of processing and receiving any certificates and documents in my name.
      </div>

      <div class='section'>
        For this purpose, I grant the representative the right to coordinate all issues that may arise in the process of
        exercising the powers granted by this power of attorney, to conduct negotiations, to submit any applications on
        my behalf, to receive any certificates and documents, to sign for me upon receipt of documents, to make
        necessary payments for me, and to perform all necessary actions and formalities within the limits and scope
        provided by current legislation for this type of authorization.
      </div>

      <div class='section'>
        This Power of Attorney is issued for a term of
        <strong>THREE YEARS</strong>
        and is valid until
        {{validUntil}}.
      </div>

      <div class='section'>
        I have read this power of attorney, its content is clear to me and corresponds to my will. Signed by me
        personally.
      </div>

      <div class='signature-section'>
        SIGNATURE _________________________________________________________________
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>